      221,
      772,
      1426,
      821
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "A. $(S): (x+1)^2 + (y+2)^2 + (z-1)^2 = 9$. B. $(S): (x+1)^2 + (y+2)^2 + (z-1)^2 = 3$."
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      221,
      833,
      1426,
      883
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "C. $(S): (x-1)^2 + (y-2)^2 + (z+1)^2 = 3$. D. $(S): (x-1)^2 + (y-2)^2 + (z+1)^2 = 9$."
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      192,
      909,
      850,
      954
    ],
